The key changes are:

1. Added a cleanChecklistLabel function that removes the "✓" prefix and cleans any special characters
2. Used standard Unicode symbols (\u2713 for checkmark, \u2717 for cross) that jsPDF supports properly
3. Ensured all text is properly sanitized before being passed to jsPDF's text() method

This will prevent strange characters from appearing in the PDF report while maintaining readable checkmark/cross symbols.
